====Pokémon Evolutions====
Selene appears in ''[[PE02|The Eclipse]]'' in her design based on Ultra Sun and Ultra Moon. She traveled to [[Altar of the Moone]] with [[Lillie]], playing the [[Moon Flute]] alongside Lillie's [[Sun Flute]] to allow [[Nebby]] to evolve into {{p|Lunala}}. After Nebby had been defeated by and fused with {{p|Necrozma}}, Selene prepared to battle the {{pkmn|category|Prism Pokémon}}.
